12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 11 O.S. 2021, Section 51-104b, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 51-104b. A. The Public Employees Relations Board is
16 empowered, as hereinafter provided, to prevent any person, including
17 bargaining agent and corporate authorities, from engaging in any
18 unfair labor practice as defined herein.
19 B. Whenever it is charged that any person has engaged in or is
20 engaging in any such unfair labor practice, the Board shall have the
21 power to issue and cause to be served upon such person a complaint
22 stating the charges in that respect, and containing a notice of
23 hearing before the Board, at a place therein fixed, not less than
24 five (5) days after the serving of said complaint. The person so
